  "Dialogue.SolariumUnlocked.Evelyn": "I'm looking forward to seeing what you grow in the solarium, dear. It's such a special place.",
  "Dialogue.SolariumUnlocked.Lewis": "I heard Evelyn handed you the key to the solarium. I think she made a wise choice.",

